title: Bug 121682: Exception throws when exporting data from a table with highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When trying to export data from the table in the attached report, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
EB: When exporting data from a table, the data should be exported without any exceptions being thrown.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Open the attached report. 
2. Add a table that includes a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 
3. Preview the report. 
4. Try to export the data from the table and observe the exception being thrown.
